prompt:

SCENE: Elena in classroom at end of day, sitting at desk with visible exhaustion

CHARACTERS:
- Elena Vasquez: 45-year-old Venezuelan woman, warm brown skin, shoulder-length dark curly hair, elementary school teacher, friendly expression, casual professional clothing

KEY VISUAL ELEMENTS:
- Classroom setting
- Elena rubbing swollen ankles
- Visible varicose veins on legs
- Clock showing 4 PM

DIALOGUE/TEXT: Elena (Spanish): 'Mis piernas me están matando...' (My legs are killing me...)

EDUCATIONAL FOCUS: Symptom recognition - leg aching after prolonged standing

EMOTIONAL TONE: Tired, uncomfortable

STYLE REQUIREMENTS:
- Dora the Explorer cartoon aesthetic: thick black outlines (3-4px), flat colors, no gradients
- Bright, welcoming, educational feel
- Clear, simple compositions
- Landscape orientation 1536x1024
- Medical accuracy with age-appropriate presentation
- Venezuelan cultural elements where appropriate

MEDICAL ACCURACY:
- Varicose veins: Twisted, enlarged, blue-purple superficial veins
- EVLA equipment: Modern laser generator, ultrasound machine
- Compression stockings: Gradient compression, knee-high
- Show procedure steps accurately but in cartoon style
